title: Ringke Fusion-X Compatible with Galaxy S20 Ultra Case 5G (2020), Clear Back Heavy Duty Shockproof TPU Rugged Bumper Phone Cover - Space Blue
features: See-through clear back shows off original design of device.
Drastically lessens impact from heavy fall damage and accidental drops.
Raised lips protects front display from potential scratches and damage.
Attach wrist or neck straps with the built-in dual QuikCatch lanyard holes. (Strap sold separately)

description: Perfectly contours to encompass in clear protection to reveal the natural shape and form of the device. The upgraded bumper technology amplifies impact resistance through meticulously designed corner supports. Each corner features an added defense structure that offers an extra layer of security.Merge a refined design with a rugged exterior for the perfect case with an all-around fit and defense with minimal bulk. The flexible TPU and hard PC makes it easy to pull out of pockets without catching lint. This case will be a stylish addition to any outfit with its unobtrusive simplicity and professional qualities. Take it with you wherever you go, whether it's to a picnic, work, school ora night out.The durable thermoplastic urethane bumper protects all of the well-rounded sides and flawlessly fits all edges. The added addition of ridges in the TPU bumper provides a boosted grip control for comfortable handling. The raised front lip prevents your screen from touching a flat surface, and the rear camera also includes an elevated back lip to protect the lens.Packed with an enhanced Anti-Scratch Dual Coating Technology, the Fusion-X defends the screen with 2x longer lasting durability against drops and scratches. The Active Touch Technology buttons are specially designed for a more natural and responsive feeling when pushing the volume and power buttons. The textured power button makes it easier to locate and operate.Newly added two lanyard holes makes the device adaptable and portable for any situation! Carry your device easily and conveniently by attaching accessories, such as finger, wrist, neck straps or even crossbody straps with upgraded QuikCatch lanyard holes to secure your phone.
Ringke FUSION-X offers MIL-STD 810G - 516.6 Certified Military Grade Drop Protection. *Phones survived professional drop test from a height of 4 feet (48-inches) 26 times on an impact surface.
